                        <p> This app works using express and Node.js. Express is a minimal and flexible Node.js web 
                            application framework that provides a robust set of features for web and mobile applications. 
                            Each API call is handled by express thought <code>express.Router()</code> define as:
                        </p><br>
                        <p>
                            <code>
                                router.route('/api/contact/')<br>
                                    &nbsp;.get(contactController.list)<br>
                                    &nbsp;.post(contactController.create)
                            </code>
                        </p>
                        where <code>contactController.list</code> is the method called when a GET request is incoming and <code>contactController.create</code> is 
                        the method called when a POST request is incoming. 


                       
                       

